annotations.title: Whiskey Rickey - the Progenitor of the Gin Rickey

textContent:
2 oz Whiskey (Rye preferred)
0.75 oz Lime Juice
top Soda Water

Stir whiskey and lime juice in a collins glass with ice. Top with soda water.
